org.jbei.ice.lib.entry.model

Class Strain

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.jbei.ice.lib.entry.model.Entry
      • org.jbei.ice.lib.entry.model.Strain
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, IDataModel

    @Entity
@Indexed
public class Strain
extends Entry
    Store Strain specific fields.

    • host: The strain host name, e.g. DH10B.
    • genotypePhenotype: Detail genotype or phenotype information.
    • plasmids: Plasmids harbored by this strain.
    Author:
    Timothy Ham, Ziovii Dmytriv, Hector Plahar
    See Also:
    Serialized Form
